history.content: Despite it being a prerequisite to declare, Stat 133 is said to be "too easy to carry much weight" for whatever reason. You can phase 2 that, but check all 3 open seating limits first!

I am currently an undeclared sophomore in L&S (hoping to early declare at the end of this semester). Next fall, as a junior, I am planning to take: CS 61C, Stats 135, Stats 133 and a 3-unit breadth course. My phase I is tomorrow and I am thinking of signing up for Stats 135, Stats 133 and the breadth course for full 10 units. However, I am a little worried as to whether I will be able to get into CS 61C during phase II. As a junior in L&S, regardless of whether I am declared or not before next semester starts, would it be possible to get into 61C successfully during Phase II? I really want to take 61C next semester so that my choices of CS upper divs will become more flexible. Thank you!
history.subject: Phase 2 CS61C?
